itemDescription: British naval commander, explorer and politician (1792-1865)

wikipedia_page.main: Admiral Algernon Percy, 4th Duke of Northumberland,  (15 December 1792 – 12 February 1865), styled Lord Algernon Percy from birth until 1816 and known as Lord Prudhoe between 1816 and 1847, was a British naval commander, explorer and Conservative politician.
